skins.shipDescription: Are you the commander? Hmm... Very well. I'm Noire. The CPU of Lastation. You can put your mind at ease now that I'm here.
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm Noire, the CPU of Lastation. I wonder if I'll be able to make many friends in this new world... B-but more importantly! Give me a report on the current state of the war.
skins.acquisition: Are you the commander? Hmm. Very well. I'm Noire. The CPU of Lastation. You can put your mind at ease now that I'm here.
skins.login: You're fashionably late, I see. We have much to do today, so get ready.
skins.secretaryIdle1: You're not neglecting my maintenance are you? Of course equipment is important, but our motivation also affects our performance, so pay attention to it.
skins.secretaryIdle2: The dresses these girls wear are quite cute. A-and I'm not just saying that because I want to try them out or anything.
skins.secretaryIdle3: Hmhhmhmmn? Hmmhm?... Huh? Since when did you get here...?
skins.secretaryTouch: Noir...! Keep your hands off me!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: L-listen here... If you don't stop it right now then I will get angry.
